{"tid":159166,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【好困擾】【JJ插沙求救】wifi長期唔穩定，好似係","createTime":"2017-03-16T18:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T14:55:14.000Z","uid":54837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94a14136bce595876275fa5ae94e404f333736b1","tid":159166,"uid":54837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:48:23.000Z","msg":"有google過，但都唔係exactly講緊我遇到嘅問題 求巴打解答。<br />\n<br />\nRouter 係 TP-LINK AC1750 , 2.4/5G雙頻<br />\n使用環境係屋企，直線距離大約10尺，隔一面牆，以下講嘅問題係不論用2.4定5G都會發生嘅。<br />\n<br />\n情況是咁的，喺房用macbook air同ipad，都會用用下突然上唔到網，但仍然connect住個signal （接近收爆/完全爆），例如macbook用chrome上網時，load緊嗰陣左下角會寫住「正在解析主機...」，如果我人手disconnect再connect返個wifi，都會即時上得返，所以估計唔係寬頻本身有問題。<br />\n<br />\n最得意係，通常macbook同ipad出事多，android三叔電話印象中冇試過，有都係極少。但係房有部pc，用homeplug連lan線上，大約一兩日會遇到一次，windows個上網icon會寫住無網絡存取，同樣係人手reconnect一次就會即時上得返。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，公司係細公司，desktop wifi上網，大約有15部win10電腦，隻router唔記得係咩model，好似幾勁，但全部人都exact7ly有以上問題，每日發生5次以上，呢個聽講係connection太多？但我屋企得幾個device，點解都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？係咪要換Router？如果係，揀嗰陣要留意乜嘢去避免呢個問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 射射 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6354b81a61301007fe76723476581074f6073f9b","tid":159166,"uid":54837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe5bab337d01107a4b8301575f5b5d4bcec9965","tid":159166,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"換"},{"pid":"c44f74746418db23bf6c90f35ec8c2a070da76d9","tid":159166,"uid":54837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6c1d5aaf6da3f5951181889445cd95f4e8a063","tid":159166,"uid":54837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:15:20.00